[![Get it from the Snap Store](https://snapcraft.io/static/images/badges/en/snap-store-black.svg)](https://snapcraft.io/slog)

$ slog_

  All the commands are implemented as plugins in the
  `slogge.commands` package.  If a python module is
  placed named "cmd_foo" it will show up as "foo"
  command and the `cli` object within it will be
  loaded as nested Click command.

Usage:

  $ virtualenv --python=/usr/bin/python3.6 .env
  $ . .env/bin/activate
  $ pip install --editable .
  $ slog --help

link to executable:

  $ ln -s $(pwd)/.env/bin/slog /usr/bin/slog
